---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import WarningStripe from '../components/WarningStripe.astro';
import NervLogo from '../components/NervLogo.astro';
import NoticeInfo from '../components/NoticeInfo.astro';
import SecurityLevel from '../components/SecurityLevel.astro';
import ClassifiedBox from '../components/ClassifiedBox.astro';
---

<Layout title="Domain Seized - NERV Special Agency">
  <WarningStripe />
  
  <main class="container">
    <NervLogo />
    
    <div class="card">
      <h1 class="title">
        NERV特務機関 緊急通告<br />
        <span class="subtitle">NERV SPECIAL AGENCY EMERGENCY NOTICE</span>
      </h1>

      <NoticeInfo />

      <div class="content">
        <h2 class="section-title">緊急封鎖通知 / NOTICE OF DOMAIN SEIZURE</h2>
        
        <p>
          本ドメインは<strong>NERV特務機関 第3新東京市特別保安部</strong>により一時的に接収されました。
        </p>
        
        <p>
          This domain has been temporarily seized by the <strong>NERV Special Agency, 
          Tokyo-3 Security Division</strong> in accordance with emergency protocols 
          established under the Human Instrumentality Project.
        </p>

        <h3 class="subsection-title">封鎖理由 / REASON FOR SEIZURE</h3>
        
        <ul class="reason-list">
          <li>使徒接近警報発令中 / Angel Attack Alert Activated</li>
          <li>緊急保安対策実施中 / Emergency Security Measures in Effect</li>
          <li>機密情報保護措置 / Classified Information Protection</li>
          <li>MAGI システム承認待機 / MAGI System Authorization Pending</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="warning-text">
          このドメインに関連するすべてのデータおよび通信は、NERV特務機関の調査対象となります。
          本調査を妨害または阻害する試みは、さらなる措置の対象となる可能性があります。
        </p>

        <p class="warning-text">
          All data and communications related to this domain are subject to NERV investigation.
          Any attempt to interfere with or obstruct this operation may result in additional measures.
        </p>

        <SecurityLevel />

        <ClassifiedBox />

        <p class="footer-text">
          詳細については、NERV本部またはMAGIシステム管理部門にお問い合わせください。<br />
          For more information, please contact NERV Headquarters or MAGI System Administration.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <WarningStripe />

  <div class="easter-egg">
    <p>もし真実を知りたければ、答えは「鏡花水月」の中に...</p>
    <p>If you seek the truth, the answer lies within "Kyōka Suigetsu"...</p>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
  }

  .card {
    background-color: #2a2a2a;
    border: 3px solid #ff0000;
    padding: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .title {
    color: #ff0000;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.5);
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #ffcc00;
    display: block;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .content {
    padding: 1rem 0;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    color: #ff0000;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin: 2rem 0 1rem 0;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #ff0000;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .subsection-title {
    color: #ffcc00;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0 1rem 0;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .content p {
    margin: 1rem 0;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .content strong {
    color: #00ff00;
  }

  .reason-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 0;
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }

  .reason-list li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0 0.5rem 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .reason-list li::before {
    content: "▶";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #ff0000;
  }

  .warning-text {
    background-color: #1a1a1a;
    border-left: 4px solid #ff0000;
    padding: 1rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #ffcc00;
  }

  .footer-text {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #999;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #666;
  }

  .easter-egg {
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .easter-egg p {
    color: #00ff00;
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    font-style: italic;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .container {
      padding: 1rem 0.5rem;
    }

    .card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .title {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .subtitle {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .content {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
  }

  @keyframes scanline {
    0% {
      transform: translateY(-100%);
    }
    100% {
      transform: translateY(100vh);
    }
  }

  body::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 2px;
    background: rgba(0, 255, 0, 0.1);
    animation: scanline 4s linear infinite;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 9999;
  }
</style>

<script>
  const logo = document.querySelector('.logo-container');
  let clickCount = 0;
  
  logo?.addEventListener('click', () => {
    clickCount++;
    if (clickCount >= 3) {
      document.cookie = 'has_visited=true; path=/; max-age=31536000; SameSite=Strict';
      window.location.href = '/';
    }
  });
</script>
